data.description: Dreaming of new construction. located in Penn school system and want that super desirable farmhouse feel? You have found it! Built in 2019 and nestled on a cul-de-sac, this dreamy 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home will make one lucky new home owner very happy. Luxury vinyl plank flooring, large eat in kitchen with island and a full compliment of kitchen appliances make for the ideal dinner party or food prep station.  The master bedroom with en-suite is the perfect retreat at the end of a long day! Or escape to the finished lower lever with an additional living room and 4th bedroom with egress window. Spring is in the air and summer is around the corner! The covered front porch is an amazing way to soak in all the sites and sounds of the seasons!
